        <scene id="30" background="CG22-1.jpg">
            <bgm src="8_24_war.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">哼……这就是五万年前，第九律者的“地”之力量吗？</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">……还真是个好东西呢，跨越世代的战利品，所谓的“神之键”。</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">……竟然可以让你这样手无缚鸡之力的家伙，也能阻挡住现在的我！</speak>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">薛定谔……</speak>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">不……“你”……</speak>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">……“你”为什么对“伊甸之星”知道得这么清楚？</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">呵……同窗七年的爱因斯坦博士……你最想对我提出的问题，竟然是这个吗？</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">不过……也好。</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">某位女武神正在被我的量子分身逗得团团转呢——我们有的是时间。</speak>
            <goto goto="40" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="40" background="connecticutFarm.jpg">
            <bgm src="8_24_war.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroSmileCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">从结论来讲……是你手上的“神之键”，它自己告诉我的。</speak>
            <show chara="schroSmileCatClose" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einShockWinterEdenClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">……？</speak>
            <show chara="einShockWinterEdenClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroHaughtyCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">呵，准确地说，是躺在里面的，已经被“禁锢”了的“核心”。</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">——“闻”过那个的“味道”，谁都能明白的吧？</speak>
            <show chara="schroHaughtyCatClose" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSadWinterEdenClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">这……怎么可能……</speak>
            <show chara="einSadWinterEdenClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroScornfulCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">我也很吃惊呢。</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroHaughtyCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">应该说……我现在比你们多了一种感官，它能够轻易“嗅”出由崩坏“书写”的信息。</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroSmileCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">所以，知道这护盾的力量属于第九律者，又有什么可奇怪的？</speak>
            <show chara="schroSmileCatClose" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltQuestionNewClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">你……你究竟还知道些什么？</speak>
            <show chara="weltQuestionNewClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroExcitedCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">哦呀。我们的“主人公”（HERO）总算是发问了呢。</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroSmileCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">嗯……让我想想……</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroHaughtyCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">我知道纽约的情况……我知道“公主”的情况……我也大致能猜出你的情况。</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroScornfulCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">啊……就在刚才，我也稍稍明白了，那个女武神的情况。</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroExcitedCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">所以，你想从哪个开始听呢？我们世代的“律者”先生？</speak>
            <show chara="schroExcitedCatClose" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltNoWordsNewClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="einShockWinterEdenClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">你……</speak>
            <show chara="einShockWinterEdenClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroSmileCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">怎么……这家伙是律者，那不是显而易见的事情吗？</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroScornfulCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">啊……对哦。你们感受不到呢。</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroExcitedCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">这家伙的每一个细胞，可都在饥渴地呐喊着哦！</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">“我想吞噬”……“我想吸收”……“我想重新打造一切”！</speak>
            <show chara="weltSBDNewClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">不……不要胡说！</speak>
            <show chara="weltSBDNewClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroScornfulCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">呵……胡说？</speak>
            <show chara="energyballSchroBackLeftClose" position="back"/>
            <show chara="schroExcitedCatClose" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">你脑子里也许理解不了——但身体，却早已经饥渴难耐了吧！</speak>
            <goto goto="50" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="50" background="CG22-1-2.jpg">
            <bgm src="8_24_war.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">快住手！</speak>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">这样下去，事情会不受控制的！</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">……不受控制？</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">哈哈哈哈，这不也挺好吗？</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">……如果还想让事情走回你所设计的“正轨”，那就让瓦尔特自己站出来！</speak>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">不可能！</speak>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">我不会让你伤害他的！</speak>
            <speak chara="schroCatNoFace">哼——</speak>
